18:47.180 --> 18:51.050
the situation is resolved and your safety guaranteed.

18:52.130 --> 18:54.130
♪ ♪

19:03.120 --> 19:05.130
-You know how to use it? -In a pinch.

19:16.150 --> 19:17.210
So what's the cargo?

19:17.220 --> 19:19.100
-I'm gonna give you a clue.

19:19.110 --> 19:22.090
We are 40 kilometers from the coast of Morocco,

19:22.100 --> 19:24.210
and I'm pretty sure it's not Berber rugs.

19:26.000 --> 19:27.030
-That's two clues.

19:29.210 --> 19:31.010
-So how we gonna play this?

19:31.020 --> 19:33.230
-When they finish loading the truck, we're taking it.

19:34.100 --> 19:36.040
If you have to shoot, aim straight.

19:37.080 --> 19:38.150
-You're not gonna back me up?

19:38.150 --> 19:41.070
-I told you, I'm the driver.

19:49.170 --> 19:50.200
-Ayudame.

19:57.180 --> 19:58.230
-Hola.

19:59.000 --> 19:59.220
-(grunts)

20:00.090 --> 20:01.130
-(truck engine starts)

20:22.000 --> 20:23.020
-Now...

20:24.060 --> 20:27.210
you are going to tell me where our money is.

20:27.220 --> 20:30.010
-We really don't know where your money is.

20:30.230 --> 20:32.150
-You are lying.

20:33.060 --> 20:35.050
-I-I usually find it best to tell the truth

20:35.060 --> 20:37.000
